{"tid":784013,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[不安撚]有個肥仔寫左封信俾我","createTime":"2018-08-18T04:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T04:42:03.000Z","uid":34489,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aebd147bed2af2bbb01dfafb46da32a4adaf5cc5","tid":784013,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:39:57.000Z","msg":"佢同我同班，今日返到班房一睇櫃桶就見到有封信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起初仲幻想會唔會係女神寫嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知一睇信入面啲字同個簽名就知係肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n信嘅內容係 : <br />\n<br />\n我係肥叉燒，你係白飯。<br />\n我係牙膏，你係牙刷。<br />\nhehe <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩屌乜撚嘢嚟，我睇到眼都凸埋<br />\n放學嗰院佢仲拍下我問我收唔收到封信<br />\n究竟佢嘅行為想表達啲乜意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252fdf0f5a5c0a7a70e8888016a6a69e7a685f6f","tid":784013,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"賢仔做咩寫信比大家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f509114fe8d3cd32c767d25aa8305695ad92e1","tid":784013,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"252fdf0f5a5c0a7a70e8888016a6a69e7a685f6f","tid":784013,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"賢仔做咩寫信比大家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ec21123eba466d9b484ece00521be936a2ea1d","tid":784013,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:41:41.000Z","msg":"@腎仔"},{"pid":"0c02c0d880b9b7201179a160ab01c38ed34b6dcd","tid":784013,"uid":116330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime